com.ibm.zrl.idmx.dm.structure
Class CredentialStructure

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.zrl.idmx.dm.structure.CredentialStructure

public class CredentialStructure
extends java.lang.Object

Defines the structure of a credential using attribute structures and some extra information such as the location of the update information, or if a credential has an epoch.
